\Psi_{i+1} & =\mathcal{P}_{i+1}\sigma_{x}\cdot\Psi_{0}^{*}-\sum_{j=0}^{i}\braket{\mathcal{P}_{i+1}\sigma_{x}\cdot\Psi_{0}^{*}}{\Psi_{j}}\Psi_{j}
